  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p>The <i><b>Widow Wind</b></i> was a ship.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Widow_Wind&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>The captain of the <i>Widow Wind</i> was <a href=\"/index.php/Bellegere_Otherys\" title=\"Bellegere Otherys\">Bellegere Otherys</a>, the <a href=\"/index.php/Black_Pearl_of_Braavos\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Black Pearl of Braavos\">Black Pearl of Braavos</a> and one of the nine mistresses of <a href=\"/index.php/Aegon_IV_Targaryen\" title=\"Aegon IV Targaryen\">Aegon the Unworthy</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiaf_the_targaryen_kings:_aegon_iv.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiaf_the_targaryen_kings:_aegon_iv.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> \n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References_and_Notes\">References and Notes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Widow_Wind&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References and Notes\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtwoiaf_the_targaryen_kings:_aegon_iv.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiaf_the_targaryen_kings:_aegon_iv.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The Wo